==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: thŏng
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /θɒŋ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /TQN/

===Noun===
'''thong''' (plural: [[thongs]])

# A strip of leather.
# (''British, US'') An undergarment or swimwear consisting of very narrow strips designed to cover just the genitals and nothing more.
# {{Australian}} An item of footwear, usually of rubber, secured by two straps mounted between the big toe and its neighbour. 

====Synonyms====
*[[flip-flop]] (3)
*[[g-string]] (2)
*[[jandal]] (3, New Zealand)

